Program: Free Thinking
Title: Sebastian Faulks
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/m0000bph
Last Broadcast Date: Thu 13 Sep 2018
The author of Birdsong talks to Anne McElvoy in one of the first conversations about his new novel. Sebastian Faulks discusses depicting France past and present from World War I to Algeria and immigration now as he publishes his latest novel called Paris Echo. Recorded with an audience at the BBC Proms. Producer: Fiona McLean. Show less